name: SquidGrow
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en: SquidGrow is a BEP-20 meme-utility token which launched on the 17th of June 2020. The owner is a day one Shiba Inu holder who launched the token hoping to provide a safe space for investors to make money, while being a part of an active and thriving community. He hopes to replicate the experience he once had as a day one Shiba Inu holder. The token has 3 live utilities. Staking, LP Staking and a lottery. Already listed on BKex and another CEX announcement this week BitMart. The team says this these will be the first of many. The core team have years of experience in the cryptocurrency space and in the short time the token has been live, they have certainly cemented their name, and plan to push SquidGrow all the way to the top.
